# Production: leave the API base URL EMPTY so the frontend calls the same origin
# it was served from (window.location.origin). The backend serves the SPA and the
# API together (http://<host>:5055, or http://<host> via the nginx LAN proxy), so a
# hardcoded host/port here breaks every API call when accessed on any other
# address. Only set this if the API is genuinely hosted on a different origin.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
